{"tid":643674,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"中興出賣華為  機密文件曝光！","createTime":"2018-04-26T16:10:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-28T05:56:02.000Z","uid":180690,"like":35,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"3a5a607bffaa03dc9a73450a197e3454662b20a2","tid":643674,"uid":180690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T16:10:20.000Z","msg":"中興通訊（763）昨晚發公告稱，「公司管理層已決定採取相關美國法律下可採取的與美國政府命令相關的某些行動」，股票繼續停牌。該段文字難以理解，內地網上盛傳，中興通訊可能暗示將配合美方調查，轉做污點證人，向美方檢舉華為違規或交出「黑材料」，以換來一線生機。<br />\n<br />\n內地業界慣以「F7」作為華為的代號，因「F7」與普通話「夫妻」諧音，即英文中的Husband與Wife，與華為的英文HuaWei首個字母重合。該段文字意思為，華為亦有從事類似出口伊朗的違規業務，但所用的代理公司質資較強，所以風險較低。文件前面提及中興找的代理公司質資代理較低，但費用較便宜，所以風險較大。該段被美國查獲的中興機密文件確認，華為同樣有伊朗業務，而且情況為中興所掌握。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180426&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=58122087 【華為中伏】中興出賣華為  機密文件曝光！\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180426%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D58122087%20%E3%80%90%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E4%B8%AD%E4%BC%8F%E3%80%91%E4%B8%AD%E8%88%88%E5%87%BA%E8%B3%A3%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%20%20%E6%A9%9F%E5%AF%86%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89%EF%BC%81&d=g0rGYIVa9wBzMQsZpoCyfgHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=af9af84b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180426%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D58122087%20%E3%80%90%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E4%B8%AD%E4%BC%8F%E3%80%91%E4%B8%AD%E8%88%88%E5%87%BA%E8%B3%A3%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%20%20%E6%A9%9F%E5%AF%86%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89%EF%BC%81&h=d42f18a3\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180426&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=58122087 【華為中伏】中興出賣華為  機密文件曝光！</a>"},{"pid":"f3ebd3da244ec21d19a1362dda90b158f67ae09c","tid":643674,"uid":42820,"like":51,"dislike":1,"score":50,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T16:11:38.000Z","msg":"美軍來了我帶路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal